{"title":"亲近农谚","authors":["古柳"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":3,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲近农谚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古柳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲近农谚  春天便不再遥远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禾苗摇曳  拨动和煦的光弦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光合曼妙  人  大地  自然"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枝桠流动的色彩蹒跚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姗姗而来的古韵依旧茁壮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信天游穿越惊蛰的沃野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采茶调浸润谷雨的酣恬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土生土长的民歌哟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悠扬而纯朴的渴盼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天  是扶犁人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不经意的一串欢笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是山娃们甩开布褂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫山跌落的嬉闹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从大山和土地开始"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从荒漠上的一株红柳开始"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴随着嫩绿的气息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在默诵农谚的某一时刻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盼春的农人用双手梳理着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春的容颜"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}